Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.31,DCMain,GENTA,0,0,0,,جديًا؟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.40,DCMain,AYUMI,0,0,0,,أهي بتلك الصعوبة؟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.81,DCMain,CONAN,0,0,0,,.أجل
